
-- ============================================================
-- Spell 200307: Unstable Growth
-- ============================================================
-- Custom debuff for Detonating Lashers (Freya encounter) at low player count.
-- Effect 1: Root (SPELL_AURA_MOD_ROOT = 95)
-- Effect 2: 1% HP regen per second (SPELL_AURA_OBS_MOD_HEALTH = 20, amplitude 1000ms)
-- Applied by ScaledEncounters_Ulduar when lasher drops below 25% HP at N<=2.
-- Removed when lasher heals above 25%.

